title: Jennifer Hawkins' husband Jake Wall shares picture with new daughter after birth
text:
Jennifer Hawkins' husband Jake Wall has shared an adorable picture of the moment he first held their new daughter, after the model gave birth on Tuesday.

In the photograph, the doting dad is seen holding baby Frankie Violet Hawkins Wall to his chest.

'Welcome to the world Frankie Violet. Our hearts are full,' he gushed on Instagram.

Daddy's little girl! Jennifer Hawkins' husband Jake Wall (pictured) has shared an adorable picture of the moment he first held their new daughter, after the model gave birth on Tuesday

Jennifer and Jake welcomed their first child together on Tuesday.

The 35-year-old model and former Myer ambassador took to Instagram on Tuesday to share three photos of their new arrival.

Jennifer has broken with tradition and given her daughter both her own surname, Hawkins, and the father's last name, Wall.

'Welcome to the world Frankie Violet. Our hearts are full,' Jake gushed on Instagram

'Our beautiful, healthy baby girl': Jennifer and Jake welcomed their first child together on Tuesday, with the 35-year-old model sharing three photos of the new arrival to Instagram

Captioning her Instagram post, Jennifer wrote: 'Frankie Violet Hawkins Wall. Dream come true! So thankful to be holding our beautiful, healthy baby girl!

'We couldn't be more in love,' she added, tagging Jake's Instagram account.

The accompanying photos showed the newborn wearing a white onesie and swaddled in a pink sheet as Jennifer held her close.

Surprise! Jennifer and Jake first announced they were expecting a child back in May

'I'm so happy to share with you some exciting news! Jake and I are expecting a baby girl! We can't wait to meet her!' Jennifer wrote in May

Jennifer and Jake first announced they were expecting a child back in May.

At the time, they shared the same photo of Jennifer showing off her baby bump to their respective Instagram accounts.

'I'm so happy to share with you some exciting news! Jake and I are expecting a baby girl! We can't wait to meet her!' Jennifer wrote.

'Thank you to our beautiful family and friends for their love and support and, most importantly, to my hubby Jake – I can't wait to see you as a daddy!'

Over the past five months, Jennifer had been documenting her pregnancy on social media, albeit sparingly.
description: Jennifer Hawkins' husband Jake Wall has shared an adorable picture of the moment he first held their new daughter, after the model gave birth on Tuesday.
authors: Marta Jary For Daily Mail Australia
